    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just that even with help, the core of it doesn't change. the friction is just part of who i am because of how the world sees me. it feels like an endless cycle of trying to survive something that's fundamentally broken. sometimes i wonder if there's any point in keepin up the fight if the outcome is always going to be this much pain.",
